org.codeavengers.common.dto.entity

Class Results

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codeavengers.common.dto.entity.Results
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, DBEntity

    public class Results
extends java.lang.Object
implements DBEntity
    This is a wrapper for a List of Result object. Each of the Result does not need to contain the name and type information for the columns, instead it will only wrap the data. This class provides context to the data by storing name and type information for the columns. The DBEntity interface that it implements indicates that this class participates in Data Access Layer operations.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    abhishek
    See Also:
    Result, DBEntity, Serialized Form
